      "span_text": "In a study of patients seeking treatment for factitious renal colic in Philadelphia area hospitals between 1989 and 1995, [CITATION_1] the average cost of a single hospital visit was calculated as $2914 (approximately equivalent to $5000 13 in 2010)."
